embeds.title: Phene
embeds.description:
Hey, I’m Phene! I’m just the average tech enthusiast that enjoys helping and tinkering with all of the major platforms (macOS, Windows, ChromeOS, etc.) I also have some experience in discord.js and Discord bot development.

I joined Discord in mid 2017 from overhearing my brother talking about it, but didn’t really enjoy it until sometime in 2018. You’ll probably see me helping people in <#385358187513118721> , helping <@396795612307128322> with his research, or posting my cat in <#361064680996864010> .

I got my first (non-managed) Chromebook as a gift in 2019. (It's still my daily driver) While exploring what all I could do with it, I came across r/ChromeOS, and eventually its Discord server in late January. I’ve since become a ChromeOS enthusiast that enjoys helping everyone with their Chromebook issues.

Feel free to message me about anything (if I’m not on dnd), whether it’s asking a question or just saying hi. I’m glad I can be on the team, and I hope I can bring lots more for a while to come.
